Description: Support for a family of geographical detector models in R. There are 8 kinds of geographical detector models 
             in gdverse, including native geographic detector(GD), optimal parameters-based geographical detector(OPGD),
             geographically optimal zones-based heterogeneity model(GOZH), locally explained heterogeneity model(LESH),
             spatial association detector(SPADE), interactive detector for spatial associations(IDSA), robust geographical 
             detector(RGD) and robust interactive detector(RID).
